#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.trapezoid.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.trapezoid"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:1 of
msgid "Integrate along the given axis using the composite trapezoidal rule."
msgstr "使用复合梯形法则沿给定轴进行积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:3 of
msgid "Integrate `y` (`x`) along given axis."
msgstr "沿给定轴对 `y` (`x`) 进行积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:5 of
msgid "Input tensor to integrate."
msgstr "用于积分的输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:7 of
msgid ""
"The sample points corresponding to the `y` values. If `x` is None, the "
"sample points are assumed to be evenly spaced `dx` apart. The default is "
"None."
msgstr ""
"与 `y` 值对应的采样点。如果 `x` 为 None，则假定采样点之间的间距为 `dx`。"
"默认值为 None。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:11 of
msgid "The spacing between sample points when `x` is None. The default is 1."
msgstr "当 `x` 为 None 时采样点之间的间距。默认值为 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:13 of
msgid "The axis along which to integrate."
msgstr "进行积分的轴。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:16 of
msgid "**trapezoid** -- Definite integral as approximated by trapezoidal rule."
msgstr "**trapezoid** -- 由梯形法则近似得到的定积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:19 of
msgid ":py:obj:`sum`, :py:obj:`cumsum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:22 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:23 of
msgid ""
"Image [2]_ illustrates trapezoidal rule -- y-axis locations of points "
"will be taken from `y` tensor, by default x-axis distances between points"
" will be 1.0, alternatively they can be provided with `x` tensor or with "
"`dx` scalar.  Return value will be equal to combined area under the red "
"lines."
msgstr ""
"图像 [2]_ 展示了梯形法则——点的 y 轴位置将从 `y` 张量中获取，默认情况下点"
"之间的 x 轴距离为 1.0，也可以通过 `x` 张量或 `dx` 标量提供。返回值将等于"
"红色线条下方的总面积。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:30 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:31 of
msgid "Wikipedia page: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trapezoidal_rule"
msgstr "维基百科页面：https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Trapezoidal_rule"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.trapezoid.trapezoid:33 of
msgid ""
"Illustration image: "
"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Composite_trapezoidal_rule_illustration.png"
msgstr ""
"插图：https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Composite_trapezoidal_rule_"
"illustration.png"

